      <title>卢比波动率飙升，印度储备银行的货币策略成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/rupee-volatility-surge-puts-rbi-s-currency-strategy-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美元走强，人们越来越猜测印度央行可能会放松对印度卢比的严格控制，印度卢比波动率的指标跃升至一年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/rupee-volatility-surge-puts-rbi-s-currency-strategy-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 06:42:01 GMT</pubDate>
